        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A solitaire ring has a special charm. It’s simple, elegant, and always in style. Unlike heavy jewellery that only works for special occasions, a solitaire ring can easily fit into your everyday life. The same ring can look perfect at the office, during a relaxed brunch with friends, or even at a wedding celebration.</p><p>That’s what makes solitaire rings so loved. One beautiful diamond, set thoughtfully, can adapt to different outfits and occasions without ever feeling too much.</p><p>At<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Lucira Jewelry\"> Lucira Jewelry</a>, our solitaire collection is designed for modern lifestyles. Whether you prefer minimal rings for daily wear or something more striking for celebrations, a well-chosen solitaire can become your signature piece.</p><p>Let’s look at how you can style a solitaire ring for different moments in your life.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Style a Solitaire Ring for Work Without Looking Overdressed",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Style a Solitaire Ring for Work Without Looking Overdressed</h2><p>When it comes to office wear, jewellery should feel polished but not distracting. A <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"solitaire ring\">solitaire ring</a> is ideal for this because it adds elegance without looking flashy.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how-to-style",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_WfQaQ4": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/How_to_Style_a_Solitaire_Ring_for_Work_Without_Looking_Overdressed.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JMmk6L": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>For work settings, clean and minimal designs work best. A ring like the Minimalist Round Solitaire Ring from Lucira pairs beautifully with formal outfits. The design is simple, letting the diamond stand out without overpowering your overall look.</p><p>You can style it with:<br/>1.] A crisp white shirt or structured blazer<br/>2.] A slim watch or delicate bracelet<br/>3.] Neutral nail colours like nude, beige, or soft pink<br/><br/>If you prefer something slightly more distinctive, the Loomline Emerald Solitaire Ring has a geometric design that adds personality while still looking professional.</p><p>The key is to keep the rest of your jewellery subtle so the solitaire ring remains the highlight.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>This grading scale runs down to <em>Z</em>, where the presence of color becomes more noticeable. Diamonds that display color beyond <em>Z</em>, or appear in shades like pink, blue, or orange, are classified as <em>Fancy Colored Diamonds</em>.</p><p>While Mined Diamonds can be found across this entire scale, Lab Grown Diamonds are typically graded <em>J (near colorless)</em> or better. This is because, in the controlled environment of a Lab, the mineral contamination that cause color are far less likely to occur, resulting in clearer stones by default.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
