            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": true,
            "products": [
              "1-cts-oval-solitaire-and-round-diamond-majestic-ring",
              "2-11-ct-princess-cut-solitaire-engagement-ring"
            ]
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Wearing a Solitaire Ring for Weddings and Festive Celebrations",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Wearing a Solitaire Ring for Weddings and Festive Celebrations</h2><p>Weddings and festive events allow you to embrace more glamour. A solitaire ring can easily become the centrepiece of your jewellery when styled correctly.</p>",
            "custom_id": "wearing-a-solitaire",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_YyBkHJ": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Wearing_a_Solitaire_Ring_for_Weddings_and_Festive_Celebrations.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_htc4FK": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>For traditional events, rings with a slightly bolder design work well. The Portuguese Crescent Solitaire Ring from Lucira is a beautiful choice for weddings or festive evenings. Its unique shape adds character while still keeping the focus on the diamond.</p><p>You can pair a solitaire ring with:<br/><br/>1.] Diamond or statement earrings<br/>2.] A tennis bracelet<br/>3.] Elegant outfits like sarees, lehengas, or evening gowns<br/><br/>The Timeless Oval Solitaire Diamond Ring is another great option for celebrations. The oval shape reflects light beautifully and adds a graceful touch to festive outfits.</p><p>Even during weddings, you don’t need too many rings. One striking solitaire often looks more elegant than multiple stacked pieces.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Le4Pmf": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "",
