          }
        },
        "rich_text_G8V6GG": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Styling a Solitaire Ring for Date Nights and Evening Plans",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Styling a Solitaire Ring for Date Nights and Evening Plans</h2><p>Date nights usually call for jewellery that feels special but not overly formal. A solitaire ring fits perfectly in this space.</p><p>For evening styling, classic designs tend to work best. The Round Classic <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Solitaire Engagement Ring\">Solitaire Engagement Ring</a> offers a timeless look that pairs well with almost any evening outfit.</p><p>You can style it with:</p>",
            "custom_id": "styling-a-solitaire-ring",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_CV378m": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Styling_a_Solitaire_Ring_for_Date_Nights_and_Evening_Plans.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_PA9wLd": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>You can style it with:</p><p>1.] A sleek black dress or evening outfit<br/>2.] A simple diamond bracelet<br/>3.] Soft makeup and neutral nails</p><p>If you prefer something with a slightly vintage feel, the Round Solitaire Vintage Engagement Ring adds charm and personality to evening styling.</p><p>Because solitaire rings naturally attract attention, they work beautifully even when the rest of the jewellery is minimal.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xH7CqU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Solitaire Rings Are Becoming a Popular Choice for Men Too",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Solitaire Rings Are Becoming a Popular Choice for Men Too</h2><p>Solitaire rings are no longer limited to women. Many men now choose solitaire designs because they offer a clean and confident style.</p>",
            "custom_id": "solitaire-rings-are",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_7YX8dw": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Solitaire_Rings_Are_Becoming_a_Popular_Choice_for_Men_Too.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_UYNgNL": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Lucira’s<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/geometric-emerald-solitaire-mens-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Geometric Emerald Solitaire Men’s \"> Geometric Emerald Solitaire Men’s </a>Ring is a good example. Its structured design gives it a bold look that works well with both formal suits and smart casual outfits.</p><p>Another option is the Golden Solitaire Diamond Men’s Ring, which has a simple but strong design that feels modern and masculine.</p><p>Men usually wear solitaire rings as a single statement piece rather than stacking them with other rings.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
