        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Solitaire Rings Continue to Be Loved Across Generations",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Solitaire Rings Continue to Be Loved Across Generations</h2><p>Trends in jewellery change constantly, but solitaire rings have remained popular for decades. The reason is simple - they highlight the beauty of a single diamond.</p><p>There is no unnecessary decoration or complicated design. Just a diamond that speaks for itself.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, our solitaire collection is crafted using IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, combining responsible sourcing with modern design. Each ring is created to feel timeless while still fitting today’s lifestyle.</p><p>Whether you prefer something minimal for daily wear or something more expressive for special occasions, a solitaire ring is one of the most versatile pieces you can own.</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-solitaire",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
